jcHx","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rechMVWAwE4l49VjQ","target":"recGEuLOhqY6PsgzE","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"rech6GZc9zgRkQcde","ref":"1Chr.26.1","text":"Concerning the divisions of the porters: Of the Korhites was Meshelemiah the son of Kore, of the sons of Asaph.","year":-1015},{"id":"recXNwOatd5pfcgYP","ref":"1Chr.26.2","text":"And the sons of Meshelemiah were, Zechariah the firstborn, Jediael the second, Zebadiah the third, Jathniel the fourth,","year":-1015},{"id":"recPUvpTYMY9BOrB5","ref":"1Chr.26.3","text":"Elam the fifth, Jehohanan the sixth, Elioenai the seventh.","year":-1015},{"id":"recCrEMiDQGgwMA72","ref":"1Chr.26.4","text":"Moreover the sons of Obededom were, Shemaiah the firstborn, Jehozabad the second, Joah the third, and Sacar the fourth, and Nethaneel the fifth,","year":-1015},{"id":"recw0vGGdovfGA2ha","ref":"1Chr.26.5","text":"Ammiel the sixth, Issachar the seventh, Peulthai the eighth: for God blessed him.","year":-1015},{"id":"recgqYhIByC60IOPJ","ref":"1Chr.26.6","text":"Also unto Shemaiah his son were sons born, that ruled throughout the house of their father: for they were mighty men of valour.","year":-1015},{"id":"recxA5wHxJMsh39zX","ref":"1Chr.26.7","text":"The sons of Shemaiah; Othni, and Rephael, and Obed, Elzabad, whose brethren were strong men, Elihu, and Semachiah.","year":-1015},{"id":"reccpET7DnWbJM7X1","ref":"1Chr.26.8","text":"All these of the sons of Obededom: they and their sons and their brethren, able men for strength for the service, were threescore and two of Obededom.","year":-1015}]}
